{"tid":1638844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高院法官：不能一時半刻斷定禁蒙面法無效故拒禁制令申請","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:54:15.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b10bda0fbeae3ce3a67e54630fde8eb19a99deb7","tid":1638844,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"《禁止蒙面規例》上周六起生效，24名民主派立法會議員同日入稟司法覆核並申請臨時禁制令，要求法庭緊急暫緩實施規例，法官林雲浩上周日拒絕臨時禁制令申請，今日下達判詞指出《禁止蒙面規例》的實施，是為了恢復公共秩序及減少暴力行為，<span style=\"color: red;\">而24名申請人均不能向法庭提出強而有力的初步證據，指出規例的實行，會造成嚴重並無法挽回的損害</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林雲浩在判詞中表示，案中的法律討論及分析極奇複雜，不能在一時半刻間就著薄弱並且零碎的初步證據，斷定《禁止蒙面規例》無效及違憲。法官認為，有關爭拗應留在司法覆核的審訊中討論，預計本月底可進行一個實質聆訊，決定會否批出司法覆核許可，及司法覆核能否勝訴。<br />\n<br />\n申請人包括24位民主派立法會議員，答辯人則為行政長官會同行政會議、警務處處長以及律政司司長。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485014-20191008.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485014-20191008.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=db83d756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485014-20191008.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=65327002\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485014-20191008.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"65a9103cf9c6e4725a445768c422d090475992f0","tid":1638844,"uid":13936,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"法官：睇唔到蒙面法帶來咩嚴重傷害<br />\n連登五毛：休息！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050736dfd06a7890d4dbda1dd22a7860937ac8d4","tid":1638844,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話想贏又話要國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家咁撚大個機會快D幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />NBA同電競係兩大重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">1.翻譯文宣 <br />\n2.Twitter</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，反共！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0a65c4f11fe589e6b0beea48a1dff384c24e54c4","tid":1638844,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"咁即係要証明俾佢睇蒙面法無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩法官嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f0ce9c2cfa02d20bc1bbc24cf55e2fc2db7a82","tid":1638844,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c426fcdc9235f08e1b6c329833e23b8afdcc4cd","tid":1638844,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"行政機關行使立法權 僭越立法會 破壞三權立<br />\n咁都唔叫嚴重？"},{"pid":"526e96b3d32c52c1dfa1552779fc1c2f31859582","tid":1638844,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c426fcdc9235f08e1b6c329833e23b8afdcc4cd","tid":1638844,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"行政機關行使立法權 僭越立法會 破壞三權立<br />\n咁都唔叫嚴重？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"三權分立"},{"pid":"f82aea389d7ea2d5dc1a0b06a5a0424158f3bc3b","tid":1638844,"uid":24009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"仲要月底先開庭？"},{"pi